Package: evomap
Title: Evolutionary Mapping of Continuous Traits
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeroen", "Smaers", email = "j.smaers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Carrie", "Mongle", role = "aut"))
Description: Tools for evolutionary mapping of continuous traits on phylogenies,
    including multiple variance Brownian motion (mvBM) estimation, phylogenetic
    generalized least squares (pGLS) regression with confidence and prediction
    intervals, and utilities for traversing and pruning phylogenetic trees.
URL: https://smaerslab.com/software/
BugReports: https://github.com/JeroenSmaers/evomap/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports:
    phytools,
    ape,
    nlme
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Encoding: UTF-8
